Package org.forgerock.openidm.tools.scriptedbundler

Class CustomProperty

java.lang.Object
org.forgerock.openidm.tools.scriptedbundler.CustomBaseObject
org.forgerock.openidm.tools.scriptedbundler.CustomProperty
public class CustomProperty extends CustomBaseObject
A single connector configuration property, contained in CustomConfiguration. The JSON configuration might contain something like the following: 

 "properties" : [
      {
          "order" : 0,
          "type" : "String",
          "name" : "FirstProperty",
          "value" : "firstValue",
          "required" : true,
          "confidential" : false,
          "displayMessage" : "This is my first property",
          "helpMessage" : "This should be a String value",
          "group" : "default"
      }, {
          "order" : 1,
          "type" : "Double",
          "name" : "SecondProperty",
          "value" : 1.234,
          "required" : false,
          "confidential" : false,
          "displayMessage" : "This is my second property",
          "helpMessage" : "This should be a Double value",
          "group" : "default"
      }
  ]
This object represents a single property in the list above. These properties define the connector's configuration properties and are the data source for generating the code to support connector metadata used by the ICF consumer.
